{"tid":50542,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"4月毒遊岩手仙台東北櫻花祭＆彩繪玻璃工房","createTime":"2016-12-22T13:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T08:12:39.000Z","uid":25250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1411cb1bfb529888e69bbc6b42e63c3487a41eea","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"聲明：所有照片都影得好鳩，但請勿偷圖<br />\n<br />\nDay1（2？） 4月18<br />\n前一晚23：56係羽田機場著陸，訓左一晚雞場睇埋日出就頂住眼訓搭新幹線去左盛岡先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211253_49f7ec04c0f0241c0f84146e8ad9afc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211253_49f7ec04c0f0241c0f84146e8ad9afc1.jpg&h=c5380349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到酒店check in放低行李之後第一站居然係animate（個陣已經餓到半死）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211340_1cbec49c355534751492d1341b225a73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211340_1cbec49c355534751492d1341b225a73.jpg&h=8dc201ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽之後向目的地盛岡城進發<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211421_d680889326733eb6e766ade9f621cade.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211421_d680889326733eb6e766ade9f621cade.jpg&h=5278a6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個日個天唔係幾開，d櫻花含苞待放，所以睇左無耐就返左酒店訓<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Mj7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Mj7.gif&h=09f79672&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211503_b51e209d007f43c6c300a7f13a2c93ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211503_b51e209d007f43c6c300a7f13a2c93ee.jpg&h=750a1171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211547_525c2803b19ccf51292db1cbf1ccbd1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211547_525c2803b19ccf51292db1cbf1ccbd1c.jpg&h=25ce22fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDAY2 4月19日<br />\n6點到訓醒左食完酒店早餐就碌左去盛岡公園影相，今日天公造美，但係氣溫得9度<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211622_c67140ed219c3c991c090668a2c263b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211622_c67140ed219c3c991c090668a2c263b8.jpg&h=4e5c5739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211639_93274b540be25443956314157f730cf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211639_93274b540be25443956314157f730cf9.jpg&h=447f8e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211706_2c112e5fa03b4f4d5fd34c0f16bb90be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211706_2c112e5fa03b4f4d5fd34c0f16bb90be.jpg&h=ae1d130c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nD花開開地，但仲未算開<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211725_82698dae9953d24c0aed73e1201f9bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211725_82698dae9953d24c0aed73e1201f9bc1.jpg&h=16656e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲未到7點半，鍾意影相既人已經帶曬腳架黎影<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOfC8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOfC8.gif&h=831a9908&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211749_0fb2b56bb32fe4dc52466ad6a5c522f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211749_0fb2b56bb32fe4dc52466ad6a5c522f3.jpg&h=45cc1965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藏拙一下，我自己有個習慣就係去旅行會畫張畫證明自己去左<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjXVJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjXVJ.gif&h=8a5b352d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211807_cb5848a034885933ca8caf9de0bf908e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211807_cb5848a034885933ca8caf9de0bf908e.jpg&h=92eee60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁盛岡市有兩個日本櫻花百大選，我就跟原定目標行去另一個櫻花百大選&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211828_16bfc33f197f759d4996566e6c860d67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211828_16bfc33f197f759d4996566e6c860d67.jpg&h=17c48f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我真係估你唔到要行山既喂<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRF5C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRF5C.gif&h=af3ecd02&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211849_49a2653281590ea4af395a46b473243a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211849_49a2653281590ea4af395a46b473243a.jpg&h=d111190c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/211904_19d75b685bcf463626db831bff70a4e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F211904_19d75b685bcf463626db831bff70a4e9.jpg&h=a5814c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行山行到一半仲要比警車呠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （佢地就咁成架警車駛上山路）<br />\n<br />\n下面回覆慢慢繼續加圖，請等等&hellip;（今鋪無死啦掛）"},{"pid":"59db5a0a204280a00cd5182d43cc096078c98153","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"我諗行左一個鐘鬆D到啦，就到左目的地<br />\n高松之池（高松公園）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/212345_26699c844ee9dcdbc88eec1a87b0bdd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F212345_26699c844ee9dcdbc88eec1a87b0bdd6.jpg&h=d22b3379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/212321_3d5733b4fee05ba4ab5b902b727c1722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F212321_3d5733b4fee05ba4ab5b902b727c1722.jpg&h=820ef21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/212217_59277bb45e569193976a86d2b95f6687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F212217_59277bb45e569193976a86d2b95f6687.jpg&h=0b462d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面個住唔係富士山，而係岩手山<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/212345_26699c844ee9dcdbc88eec1a87b0bdd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F212345_26699c844ee9dcdbc88eec1a87b0bdd6.jpg&h=d22b3379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為行完山太熱，所以就算得10度都除到得番一件短袖同黑超<br />\nD人知我係遊客就同我打招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行行下有成班中學生行出黎，班女中學生問我邊度黎，我答佢地由香港黎，佢地個個wow！！<br />\n答應左佢地班主任，上傳上網一定唔會出樣，原本張圖好似日劇咁既意境就比我破壞曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/212345_26699c844ee9dcdbc88eec1a87b0bdd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F212345_26699c844ee9dcdbc88eec1a87b0bdd6.jpg&h=d22b3379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然大家都係櫻花百選，但呢邊既櫻花樹唔多同無咩野睇我就返酒店食晏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213157_417f48851c38b581e990dd6722218bf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213157_417f48851c38b581e990dd6722218bf5.jpg&h=c158c791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下經過岩手大，見到可以內入參觀就走左入去<br />\n然後聞到食堂有好香既藍梅味就行左入食堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213242_035aba5fbb02d9d16dcfddd2a0173076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213242_035aba5fbb02d9d16dcfddd2a0173076.jpg&h=3ccda4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213242_035aba5fbb02d9d16dcfddd2a0173076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213242_035aba5fbb02d9d16dcfddd2a0173076.jpg&h=3ccda4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特急席<br />\n<br />\n日本既大學生好乖，唔會一邊食一邊掃電話，點都食完先玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nmy lunch<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213415_8fd6230e4c8e4be1332cc0236e5f837b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213415_8fd6230e4c8e4be1332cc0236e5f837b.jpg&h=3cdc9ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍梅乳酪，藍梅哈蜜瓜包（呢個好食到我過兩日專登返左黎買） 櫻綠茶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213517_695fbc5911ec639ba380cd6f42202ef0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213517_695fbc5911ec639ba380cd6f42202ef0.jpg&h=911546d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間大學有羊（拎到攝影許可）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae90da1dfe03ee05cd9a64f5a7ef9add45e192a7","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"貼錯左<br />\n真．學生妹相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213642_6b95f06c51de49413825f9e3c7d37f93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213642_6b95f06c51de49413825f9e3c7d37f93.jpg&h=94b0964a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae8c891b00cc85378bbe8f8f3a3727466c49433","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213642_6b95f06c51de49413825f9e3c7d37f93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213642_6b95f06c51de49413825f9e3c7d37f93.jpg&h=94b0964a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特急席，食完唔準座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb47015570789cc3854124de8e2ac710ccdd480","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/213911_c972ae83fc0156218f2e17dab65ef245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F213911_c972ae83fc0156218f2e17dab65ef245.jpg&h=2c3f0756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特急席，食完唔準座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2eaa85fd69ffc971d4d0436e7634a105db95c328","tid":50542,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2403b496eba578622b5cab2b7da5165943adef0","tid":50542,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"打碼做乜又唔係唔見得光<br />\n人民風景姐又唔係d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087d1e52ee0aaf0dbf634faafe925c180b500c48","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"行飽飯行左陣，返到酒店諗緊點hea到今晚再去睇夜櫻，先醒起自己上網book左去玩玻璃<br />\n呢度就唔貼太多啦，有興趣自己上網搵「趣存」啦<br />\n<br />\n我上網book個陣，問個老闆，我日文唔多在行，想問下會唔會有份筆記睇，佢地請個識中文既學生幫我寫左份中文筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你 しずえさん 同你交換份禮物同筆記我仲保存緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214250_a1b310ced7f3a0ab34c706d9dd1d6cb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214250_a1b310ced7f3a0ab34c706d9dd1d6cb9.jpg&h=64ea7fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214117_719afbc086752f1414c26e78d6cc5ad0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214117_719afbc086752f1414c26e78d6cc5ad0.jpg&h=b5307cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214328_986dd548f65b0a4cede0e1acea0200d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214328_986dd548f65b0a4cede0e1acea0200d3.jpg&h=92559a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214344_cc2eeb5a17c7e93c491020ec8e53efa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214344_cc2eeb5a17c7e93c491020ec8e53efa7.jpg&h=369936d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214357_d96cd284bfecabd10e0f2db159444cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214357_d96cd284bfecabd10e0f2db159444cd4.jpg&h=b4084b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班公公婆婆好吹得，我地傾左三個幾鐘計，臨走個陣老闆娘まりこさん仲同我講元気でね〜，日本人真係好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁走個陣已經夜夜地，返酒店執返d野就去賞夜櫻<br />\n<br />\n問朋友借部相機影夜影唔得，所以貼呢張小丸子比大家睇，人地落幾多料，抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醉醉地之後就返左酒店訓，準備第二朝去仙台"},{"pid":"8dd914b4f46ee1775bec702370ec2ccac6f77059","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"DAY3，4 4月20，4月21<br />\n<br />\n咁其實仙台個幾日已經完全過左櫻花季，我過去既目的都只係睇棒球，所以都係快送幾張就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215520_7db944c540c33549f40f3c758c049d9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215520_7db944c540c33549f40f3c758c049d9a.jpg&h=d8e92d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂天迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215541_812b721ee49a608abba1e5b651c2584a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215541_812b721ee49a608abba1e5b651c2584a.jpg&h=86d21653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215626_22005a019424b89bc16ddcc47add5dd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215626_22005a019424b89bc16ddcc47add5dd0.jpg&h=6065a330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以見到d櫻花已經散曬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215652_e80cb387d91620354b0472586d314038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215652_e80cb387d91620354b0472586d314038.jpg&h=cd0e3dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215706_177086e7e76397c1cc24b1ad2fe85b42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215706_177086e7e76397c1cc24b1ad2fe85b42.jpg&h=134bfce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n場波打左5個鐘頭56分，去到第12局1出局再見安打<br />\n興奮到全部人企曬係身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二日場波因為大雨中止左，比較特別既係我係仙台城見到魯迅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215826_9d0f61191faa9d69c2fae9c725ef367a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215826_9d0f61191faa9d69c2fae9c725ef367a.jpg&h=5520fa67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215857_79395b9aa4e56daed65734f055b3f5bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215857_79395b9aa4e56daed65734f055b3f5bd.jpg&h=2fc02be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚扑野夜唔夜呀哥哥仔<br />\n<br />\n之後我又返左去盛岡"},{"pid":"bbd5a374b3a3f8a5319f675afd5ba2c64687781a","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打碼做乜又唔係唔見得光<br />\n人民風景姐又唔係d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本人個樣，你都唔好期待啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e20e5ef803fdc9d3060aff98500130253fb920b","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"DAY5 DAY6 4月22日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">櫻花大盛開<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/220301_ecbc552c9d4c81f5d7a4d266e7f842c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220301_ecbc552c9d4c81f5d7a4d266e7f842c5.jpg&h=33f19e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/220323_54a744b0c72af1fbcd018c1da5f28422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220323_54a744b0c72af1fbcd018c1da5f28422.jpg&h=0d19c3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/220339_4962afe490dc3813e6181d7b4afe7a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220339_4962afe490dc3813e6181d7b4afe7a74.jpg&h=85d80653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/220453_bbe902b30721ac06dee7bed5d4042c95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220453_bbe902b30721ac06dee7bed5d4042c95.jpg&h=ab450953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/220559_584a5ab299ad6a033021f2c6bd8d7b22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220559_584a5ab299ad6a033021f2c6bd8d7b22.jpg&h=d0bf47d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/220735_d0815b4cb320de748704942e7c798465.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220735_d0815b4cb320de748704942e7c798465.jpg&h=e10b1463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個英國表演雜耍既人，打D LED上櫻花到，別有一番風味<br />\n佢就表演拋電鋸，不過佢話影左相唔比放上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦，比張學生妹你地J啦，如果你J到既話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/showimg.php?img=upload/2016/12/22/220816_964f149c4ee790cdee02d226f240315b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fshowimg.php%3Fimg%3Dupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F220816_964f149c4ee790cdee02d226f240315b.jpg&h=1cfd6f1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"949d48ee293a9f7609dfe9a70e64bfc4fad37e9c","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"休息小刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e19c2d0d44378c67dbef790d9eac6d9bae8b1b5","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>休息小刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老母搶左電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e5d16337d4512fc0450c737a68114b11de308c","tid":50542,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61ef94ee1e0c586d45d41fe0f11e9c04f09f973","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/234258_263635e540aa461e87180afa4b936c1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F234258_263635e540aa461e87180afa4b936c1f.jpg&h=c1386b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼返先，500yen 十足料小丸子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/234344_e28de718686241cd89c9dbd4f03c24a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F234344_e28de718686241cd89c9dbd4f03c24a1.jpg&h=249fe1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買醉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdbd01759b7a8674b6f2fd03a008df6d62d7a3c","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"個公園中間有塊平地既，入面就有d展覽咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/234541_ee95a9f0d66d2870c8b65b439717ed46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F234541_ee95a9f0d66d2870c8b65b439717ed46.jpg&h=1178b74b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/234619_6fc24aa9f9b83e92b6df4f2bd8065c8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F234619_6fc24aa9f9b83e92b6df4f2bd8065c8f.jpg&h=ee726c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旁邊就係一條直隊既攤販，都係香港人食開個幾味咁啦，唯獨是個陣已經有串燒薯片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/234708_11c98fa0164b9acbfc80c9fc710bffa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F234708_11c98fa0164b9acbfc80c9fc710bffa4.jpg&h=cf1f4eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部相機影夜景係差左D<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/234749_bacf7a84e7a57a9cd7863362f31da0d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F234749_bacf7a84e7a57a9cd7863362f31da0d8.jpg&h=a72eb071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打光上去既櫻花都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a013391ad7357d475f85982d157e6423ea3ce38","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"DAY6 4月23日 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">櫻吹雪</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/235337_9331490246331dcf439deff83561cf64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F235337_9331490246331dcf439deff83561cf64.jpg&h=87d415c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n散花開始散既一日，但同時係最靚最靚既時刻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/235520_6fd280e14fbddd2315b51cff75d4474d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F235520_6fd280e14fbddd2315b51cff75d4474d.jpg&h=34163a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以見到地下開始有櫻花瓣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/235632_43320e77b3b68122bc900c1910eb278a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F235632_43320e77b3b68122bc900c1910eb278a.jpg&h=22cd5332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本人都係繼續酒酒酒咁野餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/235731_91c9f55e44251117f74304e754e0a2c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F235731_91c9f55e44251117f74304e754e0a2c5.jpg&h=fc97634c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/235820_1cfc50d28e8111a8e0b77354db1790b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F235820_1cfc50d28e8111a8e0b77354db1790b3.jpg&h=14c37900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n櫻花瓣好似雪咁吹落黎既畫面真係靚到仙境咁<br />\n相機根本影唔到個種美<br />\n雖然櫻吹雪可遇不可求，如果巴絲有機會去追櫻，可以選擇留多一兩日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/000017_2c155e03d40f2113affcdaab5b92ceb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F000017_2c155e03d40f2113affcdaab5b92ceb6.jpg&h=c821300b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燈上面既字係盛岡櫻花祭<br />\n<br />\n岡盛另一景點，石中櫻樹，朝早唔記得去影，所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/000109_8634c63b65e235f19439aec8d427f52b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F000109_8634c63b65e235f19439aec8d427f52b.jpg&h=6a0d4109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盛岡公園係盛岡JR站行十分鐘左右到，如果鍾意座足成日無野做既日會係一個唔錯既選擇<br />\n<br />\n相仲有好多，但係選D好睇既先放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cab1dc446d38834c9e6579a0f7e4e03449a48a","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"我住間酒店同j聯絡足球隊合作放既吉祥物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/000812_d053106adb9f328d817b2e7ef365be12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F000812_d053106adb9f328d817b2e7ef365be12.jpg&h=4088b8be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/000901_ac05f920ed513972013bfdf9c2b16259.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F000901_ac05f920ed513972013bfdf9c2b16259.png&h=7dd2ffab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左DAY1 我無一日係行得少過15KM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後返左東京買野，遇到街頭歌手買左隻碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/000948_f53ad456a2d160b547967925ded1127a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F000948_f53ad456a2d160b547967925ded1127a.jpg&h=27161cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係旅行中偷偷地用IPAD PRO畫埋上色板，但係畫得太差唔貼大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/showimg.php?img=upload/2016/12/23/001033_d09d4eed24717dd19f391473c2c3e8a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fshowimg.php%3Fimg%3Dupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F001033_d09d4eed24717dd19f391473c2c3e8a0.jpg&h=6ae345cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提個手提袋係我未出羽田機場旅行前已經爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/001150_6289d46433020e692d0b39b15e2e733d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F001150_6289d46433020e692d0b39b15e2e733d.jpg&h=f3356a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b812dd3070e94a345e5366f931a545aa52742b30","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/001847_b79004d32cf2f0b5fe56e17f66b04a65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F001847_b79004d32cf2f0b5fe56e17f66b04a65.png&h=94b91cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我瘦左幾磅返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5896cf9194b45974cccb05d178f417b465c294","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bde20cf2d4e127fb9e220eca988b56ffa02f162","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282c1f2d0a33a27136fb2adf977d48f9aafdc0f5","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91125914cebd7dc1934956f78acca388e9389a9c","tid":50542,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多圖幫你推"},{"pid":"6110233b1d08265abd6aab3e9ddcb621b1384da2","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多圖幫你推</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff11b0e2e451678c6041b850aa8a80fd5a09305","tid":50542,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}